==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Moto
<hw>Mo"to</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It.]</ety>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>Movement; manner of movement; particularly,
movement with increased rapidity; -- used especially in the phrase
<xex>con moto</xex>, directing to a somewhat quicker movement; <as>as,
<ex>andante con moto</ex>, a little more rapidly than <ex>andante</ex>,
etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Motograph</ent>⟦br⟧
